resources NI(13)
notes
PIs of the SP: Keisuke Hosokawa (UEC)
We will conduct radar observations of conduntance during pulsating aurora
using the EISCAT UHF system to investigate ionospheric current associated
with pulsating aurora. We prefer good weather condition for simultaneous
optical observations.
